title: THE LOST WORLD: JURASSIC PARK trailer

sources.title: THELOSTWORLDJURASSICPARKTrailer
sources.description: “Entertaining and unbelievable” “Very good” “Cheesier than the original” “Epic, wondrous and thrilling” “The nadir” (IMDB reviews quotes). In this action-adventure sequel horror replaces the sense of wonder in best parts of the original. Jeff Goldblum leads a cast of hidden CGI wizards. Released in 1997. Followed in 2015 by “Jurassic World.” IMDB rating 6.5, MPAA PG-13.
